title: Security Plus members overwhelmingly ratify contract (Oregon AFSCME Council 75)
text: ( Source : Oregon AFSCME Council 75) Members of Local 2376 , the Corrections Security Plus bargaining unit of about 1, 300 statewide, have overwhelmingly ratified their new two-year contract with the state. Council 75 Corrections Coordinator
